## 📊 Dashboard Architecture & Features

The executive dashboard tracks, computes, and visualizes the following metrics natively:

| High-Level KPIs | Analytical Visualizations | Interactive Controls (Slicers) |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| • **Total Accidents** | • **Monthly Accident Trend** (Time Series) | • **Year / Month** Filters |
| • **Total Casualties** | • **Casualties by Vehicle Type** (Distribution) | • **Regional / Local Authority** |
| • **Fatal Casualties** | • **Road Type Analysis** (Infrastructure Impact) | • **Weather / Light Conditions** |
| • **Serious Casualties**| • **Urban vs. Rural Comparison** (Demographics)| • **Road Class** |
| • **Slight Casualties** | • **Day vs. Night Analysis** (Visibility Factors) | |

